  "description": "## Deep Component Audit — hx-spinner\n\n**Component directory:** `packages/hx-library/src/components/hx-spinner/`\n\n### wc-mcp Tools — USE THESE\n- `score_component`, `get_component`, `analyze_accessibility`, `list_css_parts`, `get_design_tokens`\n- **Report wc-mcp bugs to `/Volumes/Development/booked/wc-tools` board.**\n\n### Audit Scope\n1. **Design Tokens** — `--hx-` tokens. Track color, indicator color, size. Dark mode.\n2. **Accessibility** — WCAG 2.1 AA. role=\"status\". aria-label=\"Loading\". Reduced-motion.\n3. **Functionality** — Size variants. Color variants. Track visible/hidden. Speed customization.\n4. **TypeScript** — Strict. No `any`.\n5. **CSS/Styling** — Shadow DOM. CSS Parts. SVG/CSS animation. Performance (GPU layer).\n6. **CEM Accuracy** — All API documented.\n7. **Tests** — 80%+ coverage. Rendering. Sizes. ARIA. Reduced-motion.\n8. **Storybook** — Sizes. Colors. In button. Overlay.\n9. **Drupal Compatibility** — AJAX throbber replacement. Twig-friendly.\n10. **Portability** — CDN-ready.\n\n### Deliverable\nDetailed audit report. Fix CRITICAL+HIGH. Document rest.",
